Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將一方通行向絕對能力進化計劃…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:14.12,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(635.2,643.2)}<LEVEL 6>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對能力?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼玩意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:18.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是這裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪了  會不會是樓上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不是做這種事的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:30.09,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(721.6,641.6)}<LEVEL 5>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學園都市的7位超能力者當中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:33.97,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(670.4,643.2)}<Accelerator>              <LEVEL 6>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一方通行能達到絕對能力
